WEBVTT

1
00:00:26.643 --> 00:00:31.564
Father, look kindly on your children
who put their trust in you.

2
00:00:31.648 --> 00:00:35.193
Bless them and keep them from all harm.

3
00:00:35.276 --> 00:00:38.780
Strengthen them against
the attacks of the devil.

4
00:00:38.863 --> 00:00:44.077
May they never offend you,
but seek to love you in all they do.

5
00:00:45.161 --> 00:00:50.083
May Almighty God bless you,
the Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit.

6
00:00:50.166 --> 00:00:53.962
The Mass has ended.
Go in peace to love and serve the Lord.

7
00:00:54.045 --> 00:00:56.965
Thanks be to God.

8
00:01:05.348 --> 00:01:07.433
Good morning, Mary. How are you?

9
00:01:09.060 --> 00:01:11.396
Good morning, Elizabeth. How are you?

10
00:01:11.479 --> 00:01:13.356
Good morning, Bernie.

11
00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:16.818
Father, would you say a prayer
to Our Lady for an intervention?

12
00:01:16.901 --> 00:01:19.028
- What's wrong? Is someone sick?
- No.

13
00:01:19.112 --> 00:01:22.907
I just want us to pray for my daughter
to lose her driving licence.

14
00:01:23.616 --> 00:01:27.912
Case number 37422: Veronica Guerin.

15
00:01:30.039 --> 00:01:32.750
Almost 1200 parking tickets.

16
00:01:34.335 --> 00:01:37.130
March 10th, speeding ticket.

17
00:01:37.213 --> 00:01:39.591
108 miles per hour.

18
00:01:40.300 --> 00:01:45.388
Just last month another speeding ticket
for driving at 104 miles per hour.

19
