52
00:08:33.504 --> 00:08:35.506
What about the score?

53
00:08:36.299 --> 00:08:39.427
- First one's free.
- Well, I heard £5.

54
00:08:43.306 --> 00:08:48.561
- Where d'you get the cash for all this?
- I just say to some broad like you:

55
00:08:48.645 --> 00:08:53.399
"Give me your money
or I'll inject you with AIDS. "

56
00:08:55.401 --> 00:08:58.947
- How old are you?
- What's it to you?

57
00:08:59.739 --> 00:09:03.326
I'm writing a piece for the paper.
I wanna know where you get the gear.

58
00:09:03.409 --> 00:09:08.957
I'll do your work for you.
Come back when you got some money.

59
00:09:14.837 --> 00:09:20.134
- Fatso, don't be spending that on food.
- I'll check it later.

60
00:09:21.511 --> 00:09:23.888
- Lost, are we?
- Who might you be?

61
00:09:23.972 --> 00:09:27.850
- Neighbourhood watch.
- Yeah, well, better keep an eye out.

62
00:09:27.934 --> 00:09:31.479
I hear there's some dodgy scangers about.

63
00:09:38.319 --> 00:09:40.613
I fucking swear to God...

64
00:10:04.596 --> 00:10:07.599
Ah, Jamey, Jamey, Jamey, Jamey.

65
00:10:08.516 --> 00:10:10.727
You're an awful man, do you know that?

66
00:10:10.810 --> 00:10:15.189
