just because I got me name
in the papers and all that,

76
00:10:52.894 --> 00:10:59.317
that Martin Cahill is too posh to do
his own dirty work, now, do you, huh?

77
00:11:07.158 --> 00:11:09.327
For fuck's sake...

78
