- Did I say something?
- Don't look at me. She's your sister.

88
00:12:42.670 --> 00:12:45.173
- Warm enough?
- Yeah.

89
00:12:45.256 --> 00:12:49.302
Night. Night, darling.
I'm in the other room if you need me.

90
00:12:49.385 --> 00:12:51.721
OK.

91
