You should be after the pubs.

166
00:17:48.476 --> 00:17:52.021
- They do more damage than the drugs.
- Yeah, right.

167
00:17:52.105 --> 00:17:53.356
Yeah?

168
00:17:53.439 --> 00:17:56.818
