175
00:18:16.504 --> 00:18:19.966
Yeah, you feed me superficial crap.

176
00:18:20.049 --> 00:18:23.428
- I make you look good.
- Great picture.

177
00:18:23.511 --> 00:18:28.391
Come on. I need your help to get to Cahill.
Write me a reference.

178
00:18:28.474 --> 00:18:30.977
